## ğŸ§  What is Prompt Engineering?

Prompt Engineering is the practice of designing and optimizing prompts to get the best possible outputs from AI language models.

It includes:

* Clear instruction writing
* Role prompting
* Few-shot prompting
* Chain-of-thought prompting
* System message structuring
* Output formatting control

